name: Auspicious Mora: "Splendid Bounty"
description: A huge Fortune Coin model engraved with a motif from the Guyan Sigils, the embodiment of a special blessing.\nThis Fortune Coin, with its special Guyan Sigil engraving, was a gift from Zhongli. It is said that this engraving is the symbol of Rex Lapis, and can be used as a protective talisman.
